<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Executing a Function on Double-click Event in jQuery</title>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
<style>
    p{
        padding: 15px;
        font: 26px sans-serif;
        background: #9966cc;
    }
 	h1{
        padding: 15px;
        font: 26px sans-serif;
        background: #9966cc;
    }
</style>
<script>
$(document).ready(function(){
    $("p").dblclick(function(){
        $(this).slideUp();
    });
});
</script>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Da doble click para ver un truco de magia.</p>
    <p>Broma solo desaparecemos.</p>
    <h1>Yo no, yo soy diferente. :)</h1>
</body>
